==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Mencius|Mencius]]: Be the first to show concern and the last to enjoy oneself

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' xiān tiānxià zhī yōu ér yōu, hòu tiānxià zhī lè ér lè)

# [describes a good leader] the first to bear hardships, and the last to enjoy comforts

